longBusinessSummary: Imperial Resources, Inc., through its subsidiary, Imperial Oil & Gas, Inc. focuses on the development of oil and gas properties in continental North America. It holds 14.9% working interest in the Cochran #1 well, which is located in the Colorado County, Texas. The company was founded in 2007 and is based in Lago Vista, Texas.
